            <img class="img-fluid" src="~/css/restaurant1.jpg"/>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-item">
            <div class="text-center">
                <p class="text-center text-dark text-justify">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Morbi lacus lectus, fringilla vel ultrices nec, auctor at nisi. Proin at interdum nulla. Donec pellentesque vestibulum nulla nec tempor. Praesent mattis efficitur varius. Mauris ac blandit libero. Pellentesque dui nibh, rhoncus in erat et, imperdiet venenatis velit</p>
